---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Dopamine Lab TV — neuroscience × Japanese philosophy for the AI age. Research on dopamine, attention, focus, and the AI age.">
  <div class="container">
    <section class="about-section">
      <h1>About the Lab</h1>

      <p>
        The lab is open. Inside: research on dopamine, attention, and what it means to think clearly
        in the age of AI.
      </p>

      <p>
        We pull from neuroscience, Japanese philosophy — Zen, Bonsai, Bushido — and the latest
        peer-reviewed papers, so you don't have to. Every week, one research finding and one
        Japanese principle that reframes it.
      </p>

      <p>
        No hacks. No hustle. Just signal.
      </p>

      <blockquote>
        You don't need to become. You ARE becoming. Right now.
      </blockquote>

      <p>
        The dopamine crisis, the AI anxiety, the inability to focus — it's all connected.
        Your dopamine system is doing exactly what it evolved to do, in an environment it wasn't
        built for. The lab explores what to do about it.
      </p>

      <h2>Where to find us</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@DopamineLabTV" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">YouTube @DopamineLabTV</a> — weekly video episodes</li>
        <li><a href="https://dopaminelabtv.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Substack</a> — weekly newsletter</li>
        <li><a href="https://twitter.com/DopamineLab" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X @DopamineLab</a> — daily signals</li>
        <li><a href="https://room.rakuten.co.jp/dopaminelabtv/items" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Rakuten ROOM</a> — researcher-curated tools &amp; books</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="jp-note">
        神経科学と日本哲学の交差点から、AI時代を生き抜くための信号を発信しています。
        毎週1本の研究論文と、1つの日本の哲学的視点をお届けします。
        <br /><a href="/ja/about" style="color:var(--accent);margin-top:8px;display:inline-block;">日本語版 →</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
